{"tid":491171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TENGA公佈\"2017年男性自慰調查\"結果","createTime":"2017-12-06T09:07:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T13:14:18.000Z","uid":75969,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"04c2a24806eea11a6ac32b688dfd29ef32b3c9e6","tid":491171,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T09:07:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171206/640_67810282cb2a628c542373138e0bca22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171206%2F640_67810282cb2a628c542373138e0bca22.jpg&h=6656470a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成人情趣用品品牌TENGA，對15歲到64歲的男性進行的問卷調查，發現有33.6%的男性是坐在椅子上自慰，79.5%的人是看免費真人色情影片自慰。<br />\n<br />\nTENGA Healthcare網站上，公布「全國男性自慰行為調查2017」，調查對象為15歲到64歲，2、3月至少自慰1物的男性，共5279人。其中自慰時的姿勢排行榜，前五名依序是坐在椅子上33.6%、躺著27.9%、側躺12.1%、打坐11.5%、趴著4.4%，至於像是站著4.3%、跪著2.9%、正座2.6%等，則是被歸類在少數派。<br />\n<br />\n至於自慰時用什麼當配菜，第一到第七名分別是免費真人色情影片79.5%、付費真人色情影片17.7%、靠妄想13.1%、情色漫畫9.9%、免費成人動畫8.4%、寫真女星照片7.0%、成人雜誌6.0%，另外靠聽聲音0.8%、看電視1.4%、看官能小說2.1%，則是被歸類在少數派。自慰的方式，95.4%為上下活塞運動，不過有些男性會用相當特殊的方法自慰，而這些方式就被歸類在少數派，像是自己幫自己口交0.6%、用肥皂當輔助4.2%、沖水0.8%、給風吹0.6%、戳肛門0.8%。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171206/640_725a962367f8e822a2f9488a394b33cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171206%2F640_725a962367f8e822a2f9488a394b33cd.jpg&h=62d0b6ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171206/640_c461f03485ac72cbf4c3d543b35e6841.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171206%2F640_c461f03485ac72cbf4c3d543b35e6841.jpg&h=e1aefe8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171206/1254067/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171206%2F